* Desmonus only nods as Bloodystrikes words, still leaning against Reptilica 
as they continued down the hall.
But kissing as his next ones.
Well, as long as she fed she didn't care what she had to go through.

But then she saw just where Reptilica was pointing, finding herself just 
wondering if she could stick her teeth into his throat and then hunt down 
the other one and feed off him too before he could tell anyone that she was 
more of a predator then any of them knew.
But, she didn't really feel like running and this was was much more simple.
Desmonus nodded.*
